By Lisa Haven
Ever hear the song by Eminem, “Will the Real Slim Shady Please Stand Up?” The song, as sick as it is, leave viewers convinced that only one man can be Slim Shady even though there are lots of impersonators. Every leftist politician is labeling the conservative politician as being a Russian spy, and those on the right are pointing their fingers at those on the left, stating that they are the Russian spies. As a result, the public is left asking the question, “Will the Real Russian Spies Please Stand Up?”
Thankfully, outside sources like Wikileaks have heard the cry of the American people and answered with documented proof of just who the real Russian spies truly are.
